        <h2 class="title">New to EOS?</h2>
        <p>If not keep scrolling to <a href="#referendum-content" style="color:#cfbf55;text-decoration: underline; font-weight:bold;"> learn more about Referendum</a>. EOS is the first and fastest decentralized self-governed blockchain which encourages its token holders, investors, and developers to share their voice through proposals and voting as a means for consensus. The EOS Blockchain is built on open source software released by Block.one, called <a href="https://eos.io/">EOSIO</a>, "The Most Powerful Infrastructure for Decentralized Applications."</p>

